<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>聚满分 · 挑战日计划生成器</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', sans-serif;
            background: #f5f7fa;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35 0%, #f7931e 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255,107,53,0.3);
        }
        
        .header h1 { font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .header p { opacity: 0.9; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        
        .header .logic-tip {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            margin: 12px auto 0;
            max-width: 600px;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .header .logic-tip strong {
            color: #fffde7;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        }
        
        .card-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #ff6b35;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #fff3e0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .form-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
        }
        
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        
        .form-group input,
        .form-group select,
        .form-group textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            border: 1.5px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }
        
        .form-group input:focus,
        .form-group select:focus,
        .form-group textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #ff6b35;
        }
        
        .form-group textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 80px;
        }
        
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35 0%, #f7931e 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255,107,53,0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(255,107,53,0.4);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #ebebeb;
        }
        
        .btn-success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #43a047 0%, #66bb6a 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(67,160,71,0.3);
            font-size: 16px;
            padding: 14px 32px;
        }
        
        .btn-success:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(67,160,71,0.4);
        }
        
        .share-tip {
            background: #e8f5e9;
            border: 1px solid #c8e6c9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #2e7d32;
        }
        
        .share-tip strong {
            color: #1b5e20;
        }
        
        .machine-readable {
            display: none;
        }
        
        .category-section {
            background: #fff8f0;
            border: 2px solid #ffe0b2;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .category-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .category-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #e65100;
        }
        
        .product-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            align-items: end;
        }
        
        .product-row input {
            padding: 8px 12px;
        }
        
        .schedule-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .summary-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0 0%, #ffe0b2 100%);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .summary-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 16px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .summary-item .number {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #e65100;
        }
        
        .summary-item .label {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        
        .checklist {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .checklist-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #fafafa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .checklist-item input[type="checkbox"] {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            accent-color: #ff6b35;
            margin-top: 2px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .checklist-item .check-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #444;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        
        .checklist-item .check-input {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border: 1.5px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .checklist-item .check-input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #ff6b35;
        }
        
        /* 促销活动活动卡片 */
        .promo-section {
            background: #fff0f5;
            border: 2px solid #ffcdd2;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .promo-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .promo-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #c62828;
        }
        
        /* 预览区域 */
        .preview-section {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .preview-section.active {
            display: block;
        }
        
        .preview-content {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #333;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 2;
        }
        
        .preview-content h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .preview-content .section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .preview-content .section-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #e65100;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 4px;
        }
        
        .btn-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        @media print {
            .no-print { display: none !important; }
            .preview-content { border: none; }
            body { background: white; }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .product-row,
            .schedule-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .summary-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header no-print">
            <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="聚满分" style="width: 200px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
            <h1>🎯 挑战日计划生成器</h1>
            <p>填写基础数据，自动生成完整挑战日计划</p>
            <div class="logic-tip">
                <strong>💡 挑战日逻辑：</strong>挑战日不是普通的营业日，而是<strong>通过设计增量目标来提升营业额</strong>的特殊作战日。核心方法是：对比上月/周同期数据，找出可增长空间，为每个品类设定<strong>增量目标</strong>，并配套具体行动计划（陈列、话术、出品、人员），最终实现营业额突破。周六、周日分别做计划，分兵作战，双线突破。
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 基础信息 -->
        <div class="card no-print">
            <div class="card-title">📋 基础信息</div>
            <div class="form-grid">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>门店名称</label>
                    <input type="text" id="storeName" placeholder="如：黄圃店">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>所属区域</label>
                    <select id="region">
                        <option value="">请选择区域</option>
                        <option value="孙红梅区">孙红梅区</option>
                        <option value="陈桂莲区">陈桂莲区</option>
                        <option value="陈超平区">陈超平区</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>填表人</label>
                    <input type="text" id="creator" placeholder="如：曹祥云">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>挑战日日期</label>
                    <input type="date" id="planDate" onchange="updateWeekday()">
                    <div id="weekdayDisplay" style="margin-top:6px;font-size:13px;color:#ff6b35;font-weight:600;"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 基准数据 -->
        <div class="card no-print">
            <div class="card-title">📊 上月/周同期基准营业额</div>
            <div class="form-grid">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>上月/周同期营业额（元）</label>
                    <input type="number" id="lastWeekSales" placeholder="如：15859" onchange="calculateSummary()">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 品类设置 -->
        <div class="card no-print">
            <div class="card-title">🍰 品类增量目标设定 <span style="font-size:13px;color:#999;font-weight:normal">（可添加多个品类，每个品类设定增量目标）</span></div>
            <div id="categoriesContainer">
                <!-- 品类卡片会通过JS动态添加 -->
            </div>
            <div class="btn-group">
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="addCategory()">+ 添加品类</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 人员安排 -->
        <div class="card no-print">
            <div class="card-title">👥 人员安排</div>
            <div class="form-grid">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>早班负责人</label>
                    <input type="text" id="morningStaff" placeholder="如：张三">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>早班职责</label>
                    <input type="text" id="morningDuty" placeholder="如：负责主推、出品、试吃">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>晚班负责人</label>
                    <input type="text" id="eveningStaff" placeholder="如：李四">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>晚班职责</label>
                    <input type="text" id="eveningDuty" placeholder="如：负责主推、出品、试吃">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group" style="margin-top: 12px;">
                <label>分工说明/注意事项</label>
                <textarea id="staffNotes" placeholder="如：早班重点负责甜品和现烤包，晚班重点负责热酥和生日蛋糕；午餐高峰时段全员支援前场"></textarea>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 促销活动 -->
        <div class="card no-print">
            <div class="card-title">🎁 促销活动</div>
            <div id="promosContainer">
                <!-- 活动卡片会通过JS动态添加 -->
            </div>
            <div class="btn-group" style="margin-top: 12px;">
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="addPromoActivity()">+ 添加活动</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 执行清单 -->
        <div class="card no-print">
            <div class="card-title">✅ 挑战日执行清单</div>
            <div class="checklist">
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="check1">
                    <span class="check-label">陈列/堆头</span>
                    <input type="text" class="check-input" id="check1-detail" placeholder="如：甜品柜堆头摆放3层，进门黄金位">
                </div>
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="check2">
                    <span class="check-label">员工话术培训</span>
                    <input type="text" class="check-input" id="check2-detail" placeholder="如：每人过关，主推语：今天挑战日，XX买一送一">
                </div>
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="check3">
                    <span class="check-label">进店口号</span>
                    <input type="text" class="check-input" id="check3-detail" placeholder="如：欢迎光临，今日挑战日，现烤葡挞新鲜出炉！">
                </div>
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="check4">
                    <span class="check-label">朋友圈/社群宣传</span>
                    <input type="text" class="check-input" id="check4-detail" placeholder="如：朋友圈发挑战日海报，社群接龙预告">
                </div>
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="check5">
                    <span class="check-label">试吃安排</span>
                    <input type="text" class="check-input" id="check5-detail" placeholder="如：门口试吃台，10:00-12:00、14:00-16:00">
                </div>
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="check6">
                    <span class="check-label">目标跟进</span>
                    <input type="text" class="check-input" id="check6-detail" placeholder="如：每2小时播报进度，午间复盘调整">
                </div>
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="check7">
                    <span class="check-label">定岗主推</span>
                    <input type="text" class="check-input" id="check7-detail" placeholder="负责哪个主推位，重点动作是什么">
                </div>
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="check8">
                    <span class="check-label">其他</span>
                    <input type="text" class="check-input" id="check8-detail" placeholder="如：竞品市调、应急备货、清洁标准提升">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 进度保存 -->
        <div class="card no-print" id="progressCard">
            <div class="card-title">💾 保存进度</div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:12px;">
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="clearProgress()" style="flex:1;min-width:120px;background:#999;border-color:#999;">
                    🗑️ 清除进度
                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="autoSaveStatus" style="font-size:13px;color:#43a047;margin-bottom:8px;">
                ✅ 自动保存已开启（刷新页面自动恢复）
            </div>
            <div style="font-size:12px;color:#999;line-height:1.6;">
                <strong>使用说明：</strong><br>
                1. 自动保存：每输入一个字段自动保存，刷新页面数据不丢（第三方浏览器中可用）<br>
                <span style="color:#e65100;">⚠️ 如在钉钉内打开，建议点击下方「下载」→「打开」→「浏览器打开」，功能更完整</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 生成按钮 -->
        <div class="btn-group no-print" style="justify-content: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="generatePlan()" style="font-size: 18px; padding: 16px 40px;">
                🚀 生成挑战日计划
            </button>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 预览区域 -->
        <div class="preview-section" id="previewSection">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">📄 计划预览</div>
                <div class="preview-content" id="previewContent"></div>
                <div class="btn-group no-print" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                    <button class="btn btn-success" onclick="copyPlan()">
                        📋 一键复制发给助教
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn btn-info" onclick="saveAsScreenshot()" style="background:#17a2b8;border-color:#17a2b8;">
                        📸 一键截图
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="printPlan()">
                        🖨️ 打印/保存PDF
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="share-tip no-print">
                    <strong>💡 操作提示：</strong>点击绿色按钮，报告会自动复制。然后把复制的内容发给我（助教），我会把报告同步到钉钉AI表格【营运计划】中。方便您日后复盘，汇报。
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 浏览器环境检测与提示
        (function() {
            const isDingTalk = /DingTalk/.test(navigator.userAgent) || /dingtalk/.test(navigator.userAgent);
            const isWeChat = /MicroMessenger/.test(navigator.userAgent);
            const isQQ = /QQ/.test(navigator.userAgent);
            
            if (isDingTalk || isWeChat || isQQ) {
                const tip = document.createElement('div');
                tip.id = 'browser-tip';
                tip.style.cssText = 'position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;background:#fff3e0;color:#e65100;padding:12px 16px;font-size:14px;z-index:99999;text-align:center;line-height:1.5;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);';
                tip.innerHTML = `
                    <span style="font-weight:600;">⚠️ 当前在${isDingTalk ? '钉钉' : isWeChat ? '微信' : 'QQ'}内置浏览器中</span>
                    <br>
                    <span style="font-size:13px;">部分功能受限（中途保存、报告截图等）。建议点击下方「下载」→「打开」→「浏览器打开」</span>
                    <button onclick="document.getElementById('browser-tip').remove();document.body.style.paddingTop='0';" style="margin-left:10px;background:#e65100;color:white;border:none;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:4px;font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;">知道了</button>
                `;
                document.body.appendChild(tip);
                document.body.style.paddingTop = '60px';
            }
        })();
    </script>

    <script>/*!
 * html2canvas 1.4.1 <https://html2canvas.hertzen.com>
